{"tid":1688964,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"呢個時世⋯揾到個肯同你去遊行嘅女仔⋯","createTime":"2019-11-02T15:40:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-04T04:10:00.000Z","uid":336382,"like":193,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"decd25b8bc1c77f2a311dd1cd75573d9134c1dbb","tid":1688964,"uid":336382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T15:40:50.000Z","msg":"呢個時世⋯揾到個肯同你出遊行嘅女仔係重要過倍你捱m記<br />\n講真呢幾個月想溝女係好難<br />\n個個禮拜都唔得閒<br />\n唯有係問下佢「聽日出唔出？」「我倍你呀」<br />\n適當嘅時候保護佢或者搵定路安全地送佢返屋企<br />\n雖然無得行街睇戲食飯<br />\n但係革命下，呢種嘅甜蜜遠勝一切約會<br />\n見住佢叫口號，主動幫手⋯<br />\n兩個字，好型<br />\n<br />\n而仲扮哂野話肯同你捱m記嗰啲⋯<br />\n兄弟，心照啦！"},{"pid":"399f2411eb61071bd9ef2c59c05254b8b28de7a9","tid":1688964,"uid":249263,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T15:41:37.000Z","msg":"借位<br />\n幫手retweet<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">入 /task3</span></span><br />\n燒背 候選人被捕 消防員被警察毆打<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=2fqKJea4mGBmMEUrlbI5RDvkInyplymEwWc8t9jwBTE%3D&h=3aeb2f73\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a>"},{"pid":"97a43bcc297407e979966d98d04c9063ef72de70","tid":1688964,"uid":253438,"like":54,"dislike":0,"score":54,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T15:48:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c161b39240f205ee4a61d1cdf2cdd1a70a37dd60","tid":1688964,"uid":261330,"like":5,"dislike":15,"score":-10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T15:50:43.000Z","msg":"剩係遊行就收皮啦<br />\n係都一齊打先正"},{"pid":"4e2cf49139ee0ba9ce22de6a268b4a93bd51e469","tid":1688964,"uid":116807,"like":44,"dislike":0,"score":44,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T15:59:01.000Z","msg":"話就咁話<br />\n但係每次都好想早啲送條女返去先<br />\n不過佢每次都會話留耐啲<br />\n自己一支公 俾人拉無咩所謂<br />\n最多俾狗打<br />\n佢女仔 成本高好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e815bc2cc7109db0487da0854da31b92fcf88a28","tid":1688964